There are many tools mentioned on the station pages. This page is to help collect other resources that are not station specific.

*Co-working tables with monitors donated by Luis Montes
*[https://members.heatsynclabs.org/resources The Tool Database] is available via our member website. The details of tools may be very out of date.
*[https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Q9tLZfRkpWcy8201h225RNJsmACjsP41 The manuals google drive] has pdfs of of the manuals for many of our tools. 
*[[Hewlett_Packard_CP5525DN(BobRoss) | Bob Ross]] the color laser printer.
*[[Class_Laptops | Class Laptops]]
*[[NutsandBolts | Nuts and Bolts]] however that page is very out of date. Many new contributions have been made and it could use a lot of sorting.
*[[LEGO]]
*Lock Picking (no page yet). The Lockpicking tools are near the bandsaw and disc sander.
*The [https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1gYBJ3UQZcOdGO18274RGv0uszYdhMKQd pad printer] that is upstairs because it wasn't getting used.
